title: Gold LF Duo To Climb
body:
I am a Gold IV support main. I have kind of spread out to Jungle and ADC but I used to main support. I recently just got my 2nd account out of bronze but now I want to climb from Gold into low Plat. I am looking for a high silver or low gold who too wants to climb. I use discord for comms. If you are interested feel free to add me in game and we can do a game. 

{{champion:432}} Bye <3
